issue.title: 1 displaying over 0
issue.body: When you have zero lives left in your recycling game, the 0 displays over the 1.

issue.title: Add vsync
issue.body: This is just a suggestion. I noticed in the code that the frame rate was set to 30 frames per second. If people have a high or low frame rate computer, the frame rate can just sync to the monitor refresh rate.
